'''Mesdri'starn''' was a [[City/Legends|city]] on the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] homeworld of [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. 

It was located in the midlands of the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] eastern continent, among other significant cities; [[Liah'starn]] was located to the southwest, [[Rhan'starn]] to the south, and [[Shevre'starn]] to the east.

